&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Band 3 Senior clinical support worker&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a friendly, enthusiastic and experienced Health Care Assistant (Band 3 ) to join our dynamic Nursing Team within Blue Outpatients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have the essential care certificate and experience of working as a Health Care Assistant preferably within the Outpatient setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support the existing nursing team in the delivery of high quality nursing services within the department, with full support and supervision to enable you to assist clinical staff in delivery of patient care. You must be willing to learn new skills and attend training if required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is full time, working 37.5 hours per week and will be covering Monday through to Friday. The hours will condensed to work over 4 days&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 12th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
